Easyjet to Pay Dividend of 9 Pence/Shr After Raising Forecast

-- B y   C h a d   T h o m a s
-- 
2011-09-22T06:20:12Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-09-22/easyjet-to-pay-dividend-of-9-pence-shr-after-raising-forecast.html
EasyJet Plc (EZJ)  will pay a dividend of
9 pence per share for the fiscal year ending in September after
raising its full-year profit forecast.  Pretax profit for the year will be between 240 million pounds
and 250 million pounds, up from a previous forecast of 200
million pounds to 230 million pounds.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Chad Thomas at 
 cthomas16@bloomberg.net  